{"tid":2095242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1998年7月6日：最後一班飛機離開啟德","createTime":"2020-07-05T09:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T10:37:32.000Z","uid":48,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd3fe2a146c08ccf3c5a37403942cc543d969af","tid":2095242,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"最後一班飛機離開啟德<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n　　一架國泰航空班機於今日（星期一）凌晨零時零二分飛離啟德機場，成為這機場關閉前最後一架從機場飛離本港的班機。<br />\n<br />\n　　這班航機班次為ＣＸ２５１，目的地為英國倫敦。<br />\n<br />\n　　最後一班飛抵啟德的客用航機為港龍航空的ＫＡ８４１班機，從中國重慶起飛，抵港時間為昨日（星期日）晚上十一時三十八分。<br />\n<br />\n　　在啟德機場跑道關燈儀式前，尚有二十九架飛機飛向新赤角機場。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n一九九八年七月六日（星期一）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的地為英國倫敦</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2e0e43dfc6cd99c375fca7d3ffb51a3308728cde","tid":2095242,"uid":321345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"啲＊＊＊＊＊令我好不安"},{"pid":"eb6c966510b85ddde51374f2cf480cff7a557df3","tid":2095242,"uid":262191,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e0e43dfc6cd99c375fca7d3ffb51a3308728cde","tid":2095242,"uid":321345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"啲＊＊＊＊＊令我好不安"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"政府公告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同黨鐵緊急廣播一樣"},{"pid":"428aea68d040c98d92bcc65056f755119d2653f7","tid":2095242,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:59:51.000Z","msg":"啟德機場見證咗香港光輝嘅年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5493178c6b3f38e31e85f1edc1f597045afc31","tid":2095242,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"當年有兩條鬼佬鬥遲上機。要做啟德最後一個乘客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf295e9d59b6cf3c87590a7daed5eb41a4ee4cff